room_title: Escape room "Bank Heist 2.0" by Exodus Escape Room in Los Angeles
room_description: The largest heist in New York history occured several weeks ago at the New York National History Museum. The museum is certain that notorious villain Ray Navel is behind the theft, but the authorities do not yet have enough evidence to take action against him. Impatient with the slow progress of the investigation, the history museum has hired your team to infiltrate Navel's personal bank vault and retrieve their priceless artifact. Will you accept the task?
